{"schema": "**Datenbank-Design für Todo-Liste App**

### Schema

```sql
CREATE TABLE Todo (
    NR INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    Name TEXT NOT NULL,
    Beschreibung TEXT,
    Status TEXT CHECK(Status IN ('Offen', 'In Bearbeitung', 'Erledigt')) DEFAULT 'Offen'
);

CREATE TABLE Bugs (
    BugID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    TodoNR INTEGER,
    BugBeschreibung TEXT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (TodoNR) REFERENCES Todo(NR) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE Ideen (
    IdeeID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    TodoNR INTEGER,
    IdeeBeschreibung TEXT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (TodoNR) REFERENCES Todo(NR) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE
);
```
